platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 播放熱門電視劇和您最喜歡的節目

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Whether you’re looking for the latest can’t-miss dramas, comedies, or reality hits, Max has something for everyone. Watch HBO Original series like Succession, The Last of Us, The White Lotus, and Love & Death. Revisit classics like Friends, South Park, and The Big Bang Theory. And enjoy unscripted treats from Discovery like Fixer Upper, MythBusters, Dr. Pimple Popper, Deadliest Catch, and Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives.
Whether it's watching HBO Original series like Succession – revisiting classics like Friends –  or enjoying treats from Discovery like Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives  – Max has something for everyone.
Entre les séries originales de HBO comme Succession, les classiques comme Friends ou les petits plaisirs de Discovery comme Diners, Drive-Ins and Dives, Max a de quoi ravir tout le monde.
